## Create Desktop Widgets with JavaScript

Novadesk is a powerful desktop widget platform that allows you to create beautiful, interactive desktop widgets using JavaScript. Built with C++ and powered by the Duktape JavaScript engine, Novadesk provides an extensive API for creating system monitors, custom interfaces, and desktop enhancements.

## What is Novadesk?

Novadesk is a lightweight desktop widget engine that runs on Windows, allowing developers to create custom desktop overlays using JavaScript. Unlike traditional desktop applications, Novadesk widgets are transparent, layerable, and can be positioned anywhere on your desktop. The platform is designed to be similar to Rainmeter but with a JavaScript-based approach for easier development.

