## Quick Start

To get started with Novadesk, download the latest release and place your widget scripts in the `Widgets` directory. The main entry point is `index.js` where you can create your first widget using the `widgetWindow` constructor.

```javascript
// Create a simple text widget
var myWidget = new widgetWindow({
    id: "myFirstWidget",
    x: 100,
    y: 100,
    width: 200,
    height: 50,
    backgroundcolor: "rgba(0,0,0,0.7)",
    zpos: "ondesktop",
    draggable: true
});

myWidget.addText({
    id: "text1",
    text: "Hello, Novadesk!",
    x: 10,
    y: 10,
    fontsize: 16,
    color: "white"
});
```

